<body class="black white-text">
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <% include ../partials/navbar %>

        <!-- CONTENT -->
        <main>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section">
                    <h5 class="light">DON SCHLOSSMAN</h5>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col s3 m3">
                            <br>
                            <img class="img_box" src="<%= don_pic %>" alt="Don Schlossman">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col s6 m6">
                            <p class="light">
                                Don Schlossman is a second generation Los Angeleno. He earned his BFA in acting from Boston University. Don has appeared in films including Kuffs, Billy Galvin and Flies on Cupid. Television credits include Judging Amy. LA stage credits include Hartwell Clark in the LA premier of A.R. Gurney’s <em>O Jerusalem</em>, Billy Pilgrim in the west coast premier of <em>Slaughterhouse Five</em>, Dr. Givings in <em>In The Next Room; or, The Vibrator Play</em>, Pato in <em>The Beauty Queen of Leenane</em>, Thomas More in <em>A Man for All Seasons</em>, Jerry in <em>Road to Nirvana</em>, Molokov in <em>Chess</em> and Charles Guiteau in <em>Assassins</em>. Regional credits include Stanley in <em>A Streetcar Named Desire</em> at the Huntington Theater and a season with the Idaho Shakespeare Festival. LA directing credits include the US premier of Miro Gavran’s <em>My Wife’s Husband, Beyond Therapy, Three Sisters, A Month in the Country, The Heiress, The Merchant of Venice, She Stoops to Conquer, Romeo & Juliet</em> and <em>Six Degrees of separation</em>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>


        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <% include ../partials/footer %>

